WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Conservation projects need mathematical planning!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
We measure areas to protect, count endangered species, and track progress.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Budgets, timelines, and resources all require careful calculation.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Mathematics helps turn conservation dreams into reality.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's use numbers to protect our mountain environments!